    "en": {
      "title": "Daupadi Murmu is sworn in as the new President of India",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Daupadi Murmu was sworn in as the country's new president at the Central Hall of Parliament in New Delhi, India.",
        "Murmu, 64, is India's second female president and the first person from India's tribal community to hold the country's highest constitutional post.",
        "The presidency of India is a nominal position, and the head of state is the Prime Minister."
      ],
